Create and configure file systems
resize devops_lv and configure swap voume
on node1, resize the existing cloud_lv logical volume to 250MB

Configure autofs for remote user home directories
create a user named bobby with uid 4000, no home dir and a base dir on /mnt/netdir and a password hoppy
configure nfs autofs such that the home dir of user bob is automatically mounted at /mnt/netdir/bobby on login
note that bobbys account has been configured on the NFS server exporting their home dir at repo.rhcsa.home:/home/bobby
log in as bobby to verify

#extend /devops_lv and -r resizes the filessytem
lvextend -L +5 /dev/devops_vg/devops_lv -r

#nfs server side
mkdir -p /home/bobby
useradd -u 4000 -M -b /mnt/home/bobby bobby
passwd bobby


